title: We should go out sometime!
body: I know I haven't been the best to you Iris, but we should hang out together like old times. I know you've been busy and I've been a bit pushy but it'd be nice for us to hang out like old times again, ya know? I'm sure it's been stressful for you with your business stuff and all. And trust me things have been stressful for me too, so let's head out to a trail or a park, wherever you want, sometime, okay?     -Jacob
